<h1> Step 3: Process Stored Credit Card. </h1>
<p> You can use the credit_card_id field ({{ credit_card_id }}) to bill your customers recurringly, as you'd prefer, by for example, setting up a cron job to check which contracts/plans are pending expiration, etc. </p>
<p> On this example, we'll solely use the card token by submitting the form below to show it. </p>

<form action='/gateway/process_stored_card' method="POST">
  <label>Credit Card ID</label><br/>
  <input name="credit_card_id" value="{{ credit_card_id }}"/><br/><br/>

  <label>Amount</label><br/>
  <input name="amount" value="2.00"/><br/><br/>

  <label>Transaction ID</label><br/>
  <input name="transaction_id" value="{{ hex }}"/><br/><br/>

  <input type="submit" value="Save!" />
</form>
